Package: nterval
Title: Calculate Sample Size for Population Coverage Intervals
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Obeng", "Daniel", , "dobeng@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This function allows users to quickly calculate the sample size required to deliver 
    population coverage intervals (e.g., k-sigma intervals) with prespecified reliability.
